      "step_title": "Nasal Clusters",
      "content_markdown": "# Nasal Clusters & Mixed Conjuncts\n\nLearn nasal-stop combinations. In Kannada, the Anusvara (ಂ) often serves as a shorthand for a nasal consonant preceding a stop in the same group.\n\n### Today's Characters\n**ಂಕ** (ngka) · **ಂಚ** (ncha) · **ಂಡ** (Nda) · **ಂತ** (ntha) · **ಂಪ** (mpa)"
